<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; " ><tr ><td align="left" valign="top" class="stack" style="color:#666666; font-size:14px; line-height:22px; padding-bottom:20px; " ><div class="mktEditable" id="business-update-entry" >The race is well underway! The global <a style="color: #3ea7bc; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.pivotal.io/platform-as-a-service/cloud-platform-roadshow#cities" target="_blank">Cloud Platform Roadshow</a> began in July and is picking up speed.
