others.<br> <br> <img style="display: block;" src="http://play.gopivotal.com/rs/pivotal/images/new-platform-canon.jpg" alt="Pivotal's Iain Gray in Chicago, and Andrew Clay Shafer in London"><br> <em>The New Platform Canon: (l to r) Pivotal’s Iain Gray in Chicago, and Andrew Clay  
