<a href="#my-name-is" name="my-name-is"></a><table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="full-block" style="border-collapse:collapse; " ><tr ><td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" ><table cellpadding="40" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; " ><tr ><td align="left" valign="middle" class="text-block" style="padding-bottom:10px; color:#666666; font-size:13px; line-height:22px; " ><div class="mktEditable" id="my-name-is-title" style="padding-bottom:20px; " ><img style="display: block; padding-left: 20px; padding-top: 10px;" src="http://play.gopivotal.com/rs/pivotal/images/nl-portrait-selisha.png" alt="Simon Elisha" align="right"> <span style="padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; color: #666666; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px;">MY NAME IS...</span><br> <span style="margin: 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px; text-transform: uppercase;">Simon Elisha</span><br> <span style="padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; color: #666666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;"><a style="color: #3ea7bc; text-decoration: none;" href="https://gopivotal-com.socialcast.com/users/1060680-simonelisha">Simon Elisha</a>, CTO &amp; Sr. Manager, Field Engineering for ANZ</span></div>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; " ><tr ><td align="left" valign="top" class="stack" style="color:#666666; font-size:14px; line-height:22px; padding-bottom:20px; " ><span style="font-size:20px;">At Pivotal I&hellip;</span><div class="mktEditable" id="at-pivotal-i" style="padding-top:10px; " >Am CTO &amp; Senior Manager Field Engineering for Australia and New Zealand. My title is a mouthful, but basically I look after the (growing!) technical pre-sales team in Australia and work with our customers to understand what they are doing and how we can help.</div>
<br>
<span style="font-size:20px;">You can find me&hellip;</span><div class="mktEditable" id="you-can-find-me" style="padding-top:10px; " >Visiting customers or with a phone seemingly permanently attached to my ear. ;-)</div>
<br>
<span style="font-size:20px;">Currently, I am working on&hellip;</span><div class="mktEditable" id="currently-i-am" style="padding-top:10px; " >Hiring some great people into our team and launching the new <a style="color: #3ea7bc; text-decoration: none;" href="http://blog.pivotal.io/big-data-pivotal/news-2/all-things-pivotal-podcast-now-available" target="_blank">All Things Pivotal</a> podcast series.</div>
<br>
<span style="font-size:20px;">In my spare time&hellip;</span><div class="mktEditable" id="in-my-spare-time" style="padding-top:10px; " >I spend time with my gorgeous wife and two daughters, aged 5 and 8. I also love to read –particularly about History.</div>
<br>
<span style="font-size:20px;">Something you probably don’t know about me&hellip;</span><div class="mktEditable" id="something-you-dont-know" style="padding-top:10px; " >I had laser eye surgery “way back” in the day when many people said “we don't know what will happen to your eyes in 10 years” – I can confirm they did not fall out (but I do need glasses for reading).<br> <br> <img style="display: block;" src="http://play.gopivotal.com/rs/pivotal/images/lifestyle-selisha.png" alt="The “Because I’m Happy” wefie: Simon Elisha and clan "><br> <em>The “Because I’m Happy” wefie: Simon Elisha and clan</em></div>
<br>
<span style="font-size:20px;">To me Pivotal&hellip;</span><div class="mktEditable" id="to-me-pivotal" style="padding-top:10px; " >Represents an amazing “Day Zero” opportunity to help customers get the next layer of value from IT. We need to make IT so much easier to consume. Having lived that journey from a Public Cloud perspective with AWS, I am super-excited to be on that rollercoaster once again!</div>
